
<p><big style="font-size: 130%; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-variant:small-caps">Perhaps</span></big> you'd like to buy a flower ?<br>
But I could never sell.<br>
If you would like to borrow<br>
Until the daffodil<br><br>
Unties her yellow bonnet<br>
Beneath the village door,<br>
Until the bees, from clover rows<br>
Their hock and sherry draw,<br><br>
Why, I will lend until just then,<br>
But not an hour more !</p>
